column2: percent_filled <- meter_data %>% group_by(park, Occupant, `Asset Ownership`, energy_type_mapped, building_description, facility_type_description, unit, service_month, asset_code) %>% summarize(unique_months = n(), consumption = sum(consumption)) %>% ungroup() %>% mutate(unique_months = case_when(unique_months >= 1 ~ 1, unique_months < 1 ~ unique_months))
